info.name: Salted Caramel Crunch Gelato
info.description: Silky salted caramel gelato loaded with golden, crunchy honeycomb pieces. Crafted the italian way

info.name: Mango & Cream Gelato
info.description: Luscious cream gelato with sweet mango chunks. Taste the italian sunshine.

info.name: Blueberry Cheesecake Gelato
info.description: Creamy cheesecake gelato swirled with exotic blueberries and new york style cheesecake bits, made the italian way

info.name: Cotton Candy Burst Gelato
info.description: Tri-coloured cotton candy gelato with popping candy. A burst of italian fun

info.name: Princess Sundae
info.description: Your favourite scoop turned into a charming and noble princess. Your fairytale begins here!

info.name: Knight Sundae
info.description: Your favourite scoop turned into a strong and loyal knight! bite into your epic adventure begins here!

info.name: Unicorn Sundae
info.description: Chocolate unicorn toppers with multicolored sprinkles on your choice of ice cream. There's magic in every bite

info.name: Mermaid Sundae
info.description: Chocolate mermaid toppers with multicolored sprinkles on your choice of ice cream. A fairytale sundae!

info.name: Lollipop Sundae
info.description: Add a swirl of fun to your ice cream. Lollipop sundae comes with a lollipop, crunchy wafer roll, colorful sprinkles and more. More fun, more yum!

info.name: Mississippi Mud Ice Cream
info.description: Delectable chocolate fudge and ice cream, married by a fudge ribbon and sprinkled with brownie pieces. We've tripled up on chocolate with this mississippi mud flavour! chocolate overload anyone?

info.name: Bavarian Chocolate Ice Cream
info.description: Rich chocolate based ice cream adorned with chocolate pieces and cashew nut crispies. If it's bavarian chocolate flavour then it's gotta be sinful and intensely indulgent. Throw in a bit of crunch and you've got a truly divine chocolate ice cream treat.

info.name: Belgian Bliss Ice Cream
info.description: Rich chocolate ice cream with hidden treasures of dark chocolate cookies, hugged by a caramel ribbon. This delectable chocolate delight is like no other! sit back and enjoy this rich belgian bliss ice cream.

info.name: Mint Milk Chocolate Chips Ice Cream
info.description: An ice cream that tells the mint and chocolate love story like no other. This classic ice cream is a marriage of mint and milk chocolate pieces.

info.name: Gold Medal Ribbon Ice Cream
info.description: A heavenly medley of vanilla and chocolate, embraced by a caramel ribbon. This vanilla and chocolate combo is our dream team! a thick, deep caramel ribbon intertwines the two flavours together in perfection.

info.name: Three Cheers Chocolate Ice Cream
info.description: A heavenly combination of chocolate and vanilla married together with chocolate chips and ribbon. A feisty ribbon twirling its way through this chocolate chip loaded chocolate and vanilla ice cream scoop. This ice cream is as enticing as they come!(contains milk & soy)

info.name: Chocolate Almond Praline Ice Cream
info.description: Praline coated almonds peeping out of dark chocolate ice cream (contains milk & tree nuts (almond)

info.name: Chocolate Mousse Royale Ice Cream
info.description: Mischievous chocolate chips playing peekaboo with frozen chocolate mousse dessert. There's no such thing as too much chocolate is there? how about you triple up on this cool chocolate chip mousse ice cream with a chocolate waffle cone?

info.name: Classic Fudge Roll Cake Slice
info.description: This ice cream roll cake is a classic combination of vanilla ice cream wrapped in chocolate sponge & covered with chocolate fudge and almonds

info.name: Bavarian Knight Roll Cake Slice
info.description: Bavarian chocolate ice cream wrapped in chocolate sponge & covered with chocolate fudge and almonds. Chocolate, chocolate and then some more chocolate. This ice cream roll cake sounds perfect, doesn't it?

info.name: Red Velvet Roll Cake Slice
info.description: Red velvet ice cream wrapped in red velvet marble cake & white chocolate truffle, drizzled with red velvet and white chocolate confectionery. This white chocolate and red velvet ice cream roll cake will have you dreaming of christmas!

info.name: Lotus Biscoff Roll Cake Slice
info.description: Soft vanilla sponge cake with lotus biscoff ice cream, swirled with a cream caramel ribbon and topped off with biscoff cookie crumble. A biscoff style celebration!

info.name: Vanilla Ice Cream
info.description: Not quite like a plain jane, this is a rich, dense vanilla ice cream that you'll recommend to friends. Seriously creamy, seriously tasty, a lot can happen over a vanilla ice cream! (contains milk)

info.name: Honey Nut Crunch Ice Cream
info.description: Ice cream with rich caramel and honey praline almonds. Honey, it's nutty, it's crunchy and it's delightful. What are you waiting for? get yourself a load of this honey nut crunch ice cream. (contains milk & tree nuts)

info.name: Cotton Candy Ice Cream
info.description: Perky pink, purple and childhood coloured cotton candy flavoured ice cream. We're happy to let you know that we have fulfilled every child's wish of cotton candy ice cream.

info.name: Roasted Californian Almond Ice Cream
info.description: Vanilla ice cream with caramel ribbon and almond praline. We've put together two classics flavours with a caramel ribbon stitching them together. This almond praline gold proves that sometime old is truly gold! (contains milk & tree nuts)

info.name: Butterscotch Ribbon Ice Cream
info.description: Vanilla ice cream swirled with butterscotch ribbon. This thick, sinful butterscotch ribbon will leave you going back for seconds!

info.name: Splish Splash Ice Cream
info.description: Celestial ice cream with a dark blue raspberry and light blueberry embrace. This delectable blue raspberry and blueberry ice cream scoop with leave you feeling blue. The right kind of blue! (contains milk)

info.name: Roasted Coffee Creme Ice Cream
info.description: Luscious ice cream with freshly ground coffee. This cool coffee flavoured ice cream will delight all coffee lovers out there! (contains milk)

info.name: Hop Scotch Butterscotch Ice Cream
info.description: With a butterscotch base, this ice cream has cashew crunch along with an enticing butterscotch ribbon. Stop drooling, start clicking! our butterscotch ice cream is calling out to you! (contains milk & tree nuts)

info.name: Pralines 'N Cream Ice Cream
info.description: A vanilla base decorated with praline coated pecans and a delicate caramel ribbon. This creamy cool ice cream dotted with praline pecans has just the right amount of crunch and sweetness with a swirled in caramel ribbon.

info.name: Cookies 'N Cream Ice Cream
info.description: Classic vanilla ice cream loaded with sweet oreo cookie crumble. Classic never goes out of style!

info.name: Alphonso Mango Ice Cream
info.description: Delicious alphonso mango based ice cream made with juicy, real mango pulp. Just go for this aam-azing mango ice cream! (contains milk)

info.name: Banana 'N Strawberry Ice Cream
info.description: Ice cream with real banana and strawberries with strawberry ribbon. This banana and strawberry ice cream combination has stood the test of time. You simply cannot go wrong with this delicious ice cream.

info.name: Black Currant Ice Cream
info.description: Black currant ice cream with real black currant and raisins. This flavoured sweet treat is a universal favourite!

info.name: Fruit Overload Ice Cream
info.description: Orange flavoured ice cream adorned with exotic fruit chunks and jelly. This fruity delight is truly delicious! get a load of this fruit overload ice cream!

info.name: Thunder Hot Fudge
info.description: Creamy vanilla and decadent three cheers chocolate ice creams come together to create this extraordinary treat. Made even more special with a delicious hot fudge sauce and a dollop of whipped cream do we hear your taste buds thanking us already?

info.name: Nutty Professor
info.description: We made sure this treat is as nutty as its name. Crunchy californian almond ice cream paired generously with nuts, almonds, cashews, and raisins drowning in a delicious hot fudge sauce and topped off with whipped cream. Going nutty has never been this fun before.

info.name: Brownie A La Mode
info.description: When brownies are the answer, anyone seldom cares what the question is! meet our chocolicious combination of three cheers chocolate and chocolate ice cream on a delicious brownie cake, topped off with hot fudge sauce and whipped cream. Decadence, indeed!

info.name: Gulab Jamun Sundae
info.description: Warm gulab jamuns with vanilla ice cream, almonds, and condensed cream. A royal dessert made special!

info.name: Nutella Slab Sundae
info.description: Gooey brownie topped with a slab of classic vanilla ice cream drizzled with velvety nutella and sprinkled with crunchy hazelnut pralines. Nutella lovers' dream come true.

info.name: Strawberry Ice Cream With Strawberry Sauce Cheesecake Sundae
info.description: Baked cheesecake with very berry strawberry ice cream, strawberry topping, and whipped cream. A berrilicious sundae indeed!

info.name: Lotus Biscoff Ice Cream With Butterscotch Sauce Cheesecake Sundae
info.description: Baked cheesecake with lotus biscoff ice cream, caramel sauce, and whipped cream. Unexpectedly delightful!

info.name: Vanilla Ice Cream With Mango Sauce Cheesecake Sundae
info.description: Baked cheesecake with vanilla ice cream, mango sauce, and whipped cream. Exotic and fun, all at once!

info.name: Vanilla Ice Cream With Nutella Spread Cheesecake Sundae
info.description: Baked cheesecake with vanilla ice cream, nutella spread, and whipped cream. Indulgence at its best!

info.name: Cheese Cake Gold Medal Ribbon Sundae
info.description: Baked cheesecake topped with a scoop of gold medal ribbon ice cream and nutella spread! ultimate sundae joy with nutella!

info.name: Chocolate Lover's Signature Waffle
info.description: A rich, chocolate waffle with chunks of gooey brownie, along with chocolate chips, butterscotch, and chocolate sauce comes with an indulgent scoop of dutch chocolate ice cream, whipped cream, and a cherry. Drooling already?

info.name: Merry Berry Strawberry Signature Waffle
info.description: A crispy, sweet dessert treat! meet our toasty, crispy waffle topped with very berry strawberry ice cream, a strawberry topping, fudge sauce, wheat crispies, whipped cream and a cherry. Looking to visit strawberry wonderland, anyone?

info.name: Classic Waffle
info.description: Nothing beats the sure-fire magic of the classics. Try this warm, toasty waffle with a creamy scoop of classic vanilla ice cream and drizzled with a sinful chocolate sauce. Always a great go-to option!

info.name: Vanilla Affair
info.description: A warm gooey brownie with the world's best vanilla ice cream, topped with hot fudge or butterscotch sauce

info.name: Belgian Dream
info.description: Warm brownie topped with delectable belgian bliss ice cream and hot fudge or butterscotch sauce.

info.name: Bavarian Blast
info.description: A delicious warm brownie served with a scoop of indulgent bavarian chocolate ice cream topped with hot fudge

info.name: Choco Lava Cake Sundae (Vanilla)
info.description: For the love of choco lava! soft chocolate sponge cake with a creamy scoop of vanilla ice cream, drizzled with a butterscotch topping and covered with chocolate sprinkles. Oh, and did we mention that it comes with gooey chocolate sauce in the middle?

info.name: Choco Lava Cake Sundae (Chocolate)
info.description: For the love of choco lava! soft chocolate sponge cake with a sinful scoop of dutch chocolate ice cream, drizzled with chocolate sauce and topped with chopped almonds. Oh, and did we mention that it comes with gooey chocolate sauce in the middle?

info.name: Almond Delight Sundae
info.description: Warm brownie with nutty roasted californian almond ice cream topped with hot fudge or butterscotch fudge

info.name: Banana N Strawberry Fruit Cream Sundae
info.description: Single scoop of banana n strawberry ice cream layered with a blend of soft fruits, fruit toppings, whipped cream, and cherry on top. A pop of color and fruity flavor!

info.name: Alphonso Mango Fruit Cream Sundae
info.description: Single scoop of alphonso mango ice cream layered with a blend of soft fruits, fruit toppings, whipped cream, and cherry on top. A pop of color and fruity flavor!

info.name: Vanilla Fruit Cream Sundae
info.description: Single scoop of vanilla ice cream layered with a blend of soft fruits, fruit toppings, whipped cream, and cherry on top. A pop of color and fruity flavor!

info.name: Fresh Mango Super-duper Thick Shake
info.description: Irresistible super-duper thickshake made with succulent and juicy alphonso mango ice cream and fruity popping boba. Dressed with whipped cream and some more fruity popping boba. Definitely your new summer favourite!

info.name: Lotus Biscoff Super-duper Thickshake
info.description: The talk of the town a unique thickshake packed with flavour and crunch and made with creamy vanilla ice cream and lotus biscoff. Crowned with a whipped cream swirl and lotus biscuit crumble. A must try!

info.name: Cotton Candy And Marshmallows Super-duper Thickshake
info.description: Dreamy thickshake crafted with the all-time-favourite cotton candy ice cream. Topped with whipped cream, coloured sprinkles and mushy marshmallows. Yum!

info.name: Berry Bubble Super-duper Thickshake
info.description: Creamy and luscious thickshake made with br favourite very berry strawberry ice cream and fruity popping boba. Topped with whipped cream and some more popping boba to give you an out of the world flavour experience. Berry tempting, right.

info.name: Cafe Mocha Super-duper Thickshake
info.description: Relive the classic cold coffee experience with this thickshake made especially with roasted coffee ice cream, and garnished with whipped cream, chocolate sauce and chocolate sprinkles. You know where to head for your next caffeine rush!

info.name: Cookies 'N Cream Thickshake
info.description: Crunchy oreo cookies blended to perfection with a rich milk base and topped with more cookie crumble to create a truly super duper thickshake. Yum!

info.name: Roasted Coffee Creme Milkshake
info.description: For all coffee lovers! a milkshake made with rich, freshly ground coffee ice cream

info.name: Mississippi Mud Milkshake
info.description: Everyone's favourite mississippi mud ice cream, now also available as a milkshake! chocolate fudge, ice cream, a fudge ribbon, and brownie pieces we guarantee an abundance of chocolate in every sip

info.name: Dutch Chocolate Milkshake
info.description: An irresistible milkshake with chocolate ice cream and a distinct hint of cocoa. We call this the mother of all our chocolate creations!

info.name: Belgian Bliss Milkshake
info.description: A rich chocolate milkshake with ice cream, dark chocolate cookies, and a caramel ribbon. Every sip feels like a sweet hug!

info.name: Bavarian Chocolate Milkshake
info.description: An intensely indulgent chocolate milkshake with ice cream, chocolate pieces, and cashew nut crispies. Crunchy, divine, and sinful all at once!

info.name: Three Cheers Chocolate Milkshake
info.description: A heavenly milkshake made with a blend of chocolate and vanilla ice cream, chocolate chips, and a chocolate ribbon. More tempting than you could imagine!

info.name: Gold Medal Ribbon Milkshake
info.description: A delightful medley of vanilla and chocolate, and a sweet caramel ribbon- this is a milkshake that's your dream come true!

info.name: Mint Milk Chocolate Chips Milkshake
info.description: A milkshake that tells the love story of mint and chocolate like nobody else! this classic flavour will make every mint and milk chocolate fans day.

info.name: Vanilla Milkshake
info.description: A classic that never goes out of style! a rich milkshake made with smooth, creamy vanilla ice cream.

info.name: Cotton Candy Milkshake
info.description: A throwback to your childhood favorite! milkshake with pink, purple and childhood-colored cotton candy ice cream

info.name: Honey Nut Crunch Milkshake
info.description: A milkshake made with rich caramel and honey praline almond ice cream. Honey, it's nutty, crunchy, and delicious!

info.name: Roasted Californian Almond Milkshake
info.description: A delightful milkshake made with vanilla ice cream, a caramel ribbon, and almond praline. A flavour you're not likely to forget!

info.name: Hop Scotch Butterscotch Milkshake
info.description: A tempting milkshake with a butterscotch base, fun cashew crunch, and an enticing butterscotch ribbon. Heaven is calling, are you going to answer?

info.name: Pralines & Cream Milkshake
info.description: The perfect blend of crunch and sweetness! a milkshake with a vanilla base, praline coated pecans, and a delicate caramel ribbon is just what you needed.

info.name: Fresh Alphonso Mango Milkshake
info.description: Everyone's favourite milkshake! delicious alphonso mango ice cream and juicy, real mango pulp blended to perfection in a glass.

info.name: Fresh Very Berry Strawberry Milkshake
info.description: Berrilicious strawberry indulgence in a glass! this milkshake with strawberry ice cream and real strawberry pieces will always be an all-time favourite.

info.name: Black Currant Milkshake
info.description: A sweet treat like never before! a black currant milkshake with black currant ice cream and real black currants and raisins. Perfection.

info.name: Fruit Overload Milkshake
info.description: An overload of happyness in a glass! this milkshake comes with orange ice cream, exotic fruit chunks, and jiggling jelly. A delicious fruity delight!

info.name: Banana 'N Strawberry Milkshake
info.description: A duo that has stood the test of time! a milkshake with real bananas & strawberry ice cream, and a sweet strawberry ribbon.

info.name: Snickers Milkshake With Snickers Ice Cream
info.description: Snickers caramel ice cream blended with snickers chocolate chunks and creamy vanilla milk. Grab your snickers snack today!

info.name: Snickers Milkshake With Dutch Chocolate Ice Cream
info.description: Decadent dutch chocolate ice cream blended with snickers chocolate chunks and creamy vanilla milk. Snack on snickers milkshake today!
